1) Install dependencies: libmpeg2, libmpg123, liba52, libde265

  On Debian/Ubuntu:

  > sudo apt-get install libmpeg2-4-dev libmpg123-dev liba52-0.7.4-dev libde265-dev

  Or, get the source code for each package and build,install:

  > make; sudo make install

2) Then, build this package:

  > make

3) And finally install it:

  > sudo make install

  You can use PREFIX= to install the package somewhere other than /usr/local

  > sudo make install PREFIX=/home/ryan
